73
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:00,879
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što se volimo.

74
00:10:02,559 --> 00:10:03,039
[UNKNOWN] Super odgovor.

75
00:10:04,559 --> 00:10:08,000
