125
00:17:37,599 --> 00:17:39,359
[SPEAKER_01] Došao sam do glavnog razloga.

126
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:40,880
[SPEAKER_01] I znate kako ja to zovem?

127
00:17:41,119 --> 00:17:45,839
